0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T16:40:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>XPS 13 加ubuntu<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我認為呢個係最識玩既選擇<br />\n老實講Windows laptop 既硬件要搵一定搵到拍得住macbook既型號<br />\nDell xps 13/15係好例子<br />\nLenovo Thinkpad系列更是經典<br />\n用macbook其中一個優點係佢既穩定性<br />\n呢方面硬件軟件都有關<br />\n你要一部硬件同mac同級既laptop行住個垃圾windows同部mac鬥<br />\n玩咩點鬥呀個OS輸咁多<br />\n換個linux上去真係會唔同曬<br />\n（用windows既各位可以試下，用linux應該會冇咁食電）<br />\n<br />\nWindows laptop既死因正正係個windows<br />\n肯用linux既話macOS既所謂優勢其實已經經好多<br />\n考慮埋價錢一定抵玩過macbook<br />\n<br />\n利申 用緊macbook pro<br />\n會dual boot行ubuntu</blockquote><br />\nWindows laptops 嘅一大缺點: OS"},{"pid":"64e382c3793c995f78894cc36b5851c23812fe0c","tid":49365,"uid":1888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T16:41:45.000Z","msg":"macbook唔係唔好，但我自己日常生活需要要機多，同埋mac機比你裝windows都係實比人笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0a36802f2a499c45faa4dfd7b0d0d35a9670c7a","tid":49365,"uid":1888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T16:42:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>macbook唔係唔好，但我自己日常生活需要<span style=\"color: red;\">要</span>機多，同埋mac機比你裝windows都係實比人笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nwin"},{"pid":"d1a1a22a05e1357af5e933348d4963bd14ceafd1","tid":49365,"uid":42912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T17:54:14.000Z","msg":"講真用windows 機真係自己攞黎賤<br />\n先唔講佢d privacy settings有幾仆街 連你打既每一個字 做既每一樣野都想偷<br />\n再者你估做做下野彈個藍mon + Your PC ran into problem好爽咩<br />\nAnniversary update之後就仲反智 Cortana唔用想disable? 唔得. 用用下想restart ? 問過system update未？<br />\n仲要佢d drivers 又係煩 總有一日係會出問題 只係你唔知幾時姐<br />\n回頭是岸呀施主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 win機用家 恨不得佢快啲壞"},{"p